data.description:
Country Living at its best with this Semi-Custom Pinyon model Ranch that sits on a impressive 2.8 acre lot in Crestwood Estates. Upon entrance of the home you find a big welcoming covered patio perfect for admiring the charming neighborhood. Entering the home you find a large living room with newer carpet, vaulted ceilings and open concept office area. Moving into the well appointed kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steal appliances, and walk in pantry you immediately feel like your home. You find 3 bedrooms on the main level with the 2 secondary bedrooms sharing a bathroom jack-in-jill style. The primary has a walk in closet, amazing upgraded tile flooring in bathroom and a soaking bathtub. 
Laundry/Mud room on main level and attaches to the extended finished 3 car garage. Home also boasts new roof in 2022, 220 electrical upgrade, hot tub prewire and dedicated switches for your holiday lighting. 
The fully finished basement has plenty of storage, gun room, home gym and movie theater!! The basement also has separate living quarters perfect for multigenerational living with private second Livingroom, bathroom & bedroom. 
Moving outside you will be delighted to know you can have your RV/Campers/Boats right on property. Bring your feathered friends too! 50x50 chicken run with 2 coops, 10x10 duck pin with shelter. Backyard has a stunning extended covered patio and fenced for perfect for your 4legged family.
